---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Pagination from '../../../components/Pagination.astro';
const base = '/portfolio';
const previous = 'elevator';
const next = 'hashes';
---
<BaseLayout title="Huffman Compression | ADEN Project" base={base}>
  <Pagination base={base} section="projects/aden" previous={previous} next={next} />
  <h1>Huffman Compression</h1>

  <section style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <p>
      Implemented Huffman coding to produce prefix-free variable-length codes based on symbol frequency. The implementation supports encoding and decoding with validation tests to ensure lossless restoration.
    </p>
    <img src={`${base}/images/wheel-shaft-drawing.png`} alt="Huffman algorithm visual placeholder" style="width:100%; max-width:720px; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid #ddd; margin-top:1rem;" />
  </section>

  <section id="phases" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h2>Project Phases</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Collect sample inputs and compute frequency tables.</li>
      <li>Construct Huffman tree and assign prefix codes.</li>
      <li>Implement encoder/decoder and create test harnesses.</li>
      <li>Measure compression ratios and analyze overheads.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section id="analysis" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h2>Summary of Analysis</h2>
    <p>
      Compression results show large gains for repetitive datasets. Small inputs may not compress well due to metadata overhead. The project reinforced tradeoffs between compression ratio and implementation complexity.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="reflections" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h2>Key Learnings & Reflections</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Prefix-free encoding ensures unique decodability without separators.</li>
      <li>Frequency analysis drives encoding efficiency—profiling inputs helps choose strategies.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <strong>Reflection:</strong>
      <a href={`${base}/documents/reflections/html/${encodeURIComponent('Reflection - HuffmanCompression 1.html')}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener">HTML</a>
      {' '}|{' '}
      <a href={`${base}/documents/reflections/pdf/${encodeURIComponent('Reflection - HuffmanCompression 1.pdf')}`} download target="_blank" rel="noopener">PDF</a>
    </p>
    <p><a href={`${base}/aden-course`} style="color:#0055aa; text-decoration:underline;">← Back to ADEN Course</a></p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>